 between the t$_{2g}$ and e$_g$ states share many\nsimilarities among different materials. However, the RIXS spectra due to the\ntransitions between the spin-orbit-split t$_{2g}$ levels vary widely depending\non the oxidation state and electronic bandwidths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2018 16:48:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-10"}
