cking. The observed effects clearly underpin\nthe perspective of building novel highly non-linear valleytronic devices based\non light-matter fluids, coherent bosonic light sources based on atomically thin\nmaterials, and paves the way towards studying materials with unconventional\ntopological properties in the framework of bosonic condensation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2018 17:46:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
