ths of\nthe initial string structures in the AMPT model. The decorrelation effects are\ntypically larger at lower collision energies and in more peripheral collisions\ndue to shorter lengths of the string structures in the initial states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 May 2018 00:37:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Aug 2018 08:35:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-29"}
